=====================================

**Cancelled Tender Notice**
-------------------------

### Mandatory Information

* **Tender Reference:** PW-_HAL-410-11566
* **Request for Proposal (RFP) Number:** F6839-215074/C

### Key Details

* **Publication Date:** August 26, 2022
* **Tender Closing Date:** September 13, 2022 (13:00:00)
* **Tender Status:** Cancelled (Annulé)

### Contract Information

* **Contracting Entity:** Public Works and Government Services Canada (Travaux publics et Services gouvernementaux Canada)
* **End User Entity:** Fisheries and Oceans Canada (Pêches et Océans Canada)

### Trade Agreements

This tender is subject to the following trade agreements:

* Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
* World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)
* Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
* Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA)
* Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)

### Regions of Delivery

The tender will be delivered to Nova Scotia (Nouvelle-Écosse).

### Contact Information

For further information, please contact:

Mariam Assal
Public Works and Government Services Canada
Phone: (902) 233-0685
Fax: (902) 496-5016
Email: [mariam.assal@pwgsc-tpsgc.gc.ca](mailto:mariam.assal@pwgsc-tpsgc.gc.ca)

**Collection Added:** None
